-to-headline-hinterland-festival-2024-3574104">Hinterland</a> 。</p><p>该乐队最近在德克萨斯州奥斯汀举行了一场特别演出，拉开了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/vampire-weekend-announce-massive-2024-north-american-tour-buy-tickets-3588656">一系列北美约会的序幕</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-vampire-weekend-play-special-eclipse-gig-debut-new-songs-cover-phoenix-chromeo-3615183">，演出恰逢日全食</a>。</p><p>此后，他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/vampire-weekend-join-coachella-2024-weekend-one-line-up-at-last-minute-3615769">在 2024 年科切拉音乐节的第一个周末最后一刻亮相</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-paris-hilton-crash-vampire-weekends-coachella-2024-set-to-play-cornhole-3617987">帕丽斯·希尔顿 (Paris Hilton) 也与他们一起登台</a>。</p><p> <em>《NME》</em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/vampire-weekend-only-god-was-above-us-review-3613120">对《Only God Was Over Us》的四星评论</a>中写道：“这是一种雄心勃勃的声音混合物，似乎不存在于同一领域，但在科尼格日益阴沉的声音下自然地交织在一起。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/vampire-weekend-add-extra-brixton-academy-show-to-2024-uk-and-ireland-tour-buy-tickets-3749797">《吸血鬼周末》在 2024 年英国和爱尔兰巡演中增加了额外的布里克斯顿学院演出，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
